    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Affordable Project Car \u2014 Great Opportunity for the Right Buyer!** If you're handy with repairs or need a budget-friendly ride to get you by, this could be your next project! This car is in poor condition \u2014 it has visible wear, body damage, and will require mechanical attention before it's fully road-ready. That said, the price reflects exactly what you're getting, and there's real value here for a DIY enthusiast or someone in need of parts. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly Fixer or Basic Runner \u2014 An Honest Deal for the Right Buyer! This used car is in poor condition, and we're upfront about that \u2014 it shows its age and has seen better days. There are noticeable mechanical and cosmetic issues that will need attention, so it's best suited for a handy buyer, a project enthusiast, or someone who just needs basic point-A-to-point-B transportation on a very tight budget. What it lacks in polish, it makes up for in price \u2014 this is one of the most affordable options you'll find on the lot. If you're mechanically inclined or simply need something to get around without breaking the bank, this could be your opportunity!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good, solid condition \u2014 a dependable used car that has been well-maintained and presents itself nicely without claiming to be perfect. The exterior shows only minor, age-appropriate wear such as light surface scratches or small scuffs that are consistent with normal daily use; there are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing modest wear on high-contact areas but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably and has been kept in proper working order \u2014 this is a car you can drive with confidence. All major systems including the engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics are in good working condition. This is an honest, everyday driver that offers real value for a buyer looking for a quality used vehicle without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $20,000, a price that honestly reflects its fair overall condition. It is fully drivable and functional, but buyers should go in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 there are visible scratches, some paint fading, and a few small dents or dings consistent with years of regular use. The interior is intact but shows its age: upholstery has wear marks, some trim pieces may show cracking or discoloration, and the overall cabin feel is well-used rather than fresh. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some service attention in the near future \u2014 think routine maintenance items or minor repairs that a competent mechanic can address without major expense. All major systems (engine, transmission, brakes, steering) are operational. This is an honest, straightforward vehicle suited for a buyer who wants reliable transportation at an accessible price and doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or an affordable runabout? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 and we're being completely upfront about that! The exterior shows significant wear, with noticeable dents, scratches, and rust in several areas. The interior has seen better days, with worn upholstery and some damaged trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs but will likely need attention and repairs to get it performing reliably. If you're a hands-on buyer, a DIY mechanic, or just need basic transportation and don't mind putting in some work, this could be your next project! Sold as-is at a price that reflects exactly what it is.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
